    "content": "@CoreFX Sky Shader (wip)\n\nBefore (1.2) / after\n\nThis shader replaces timecycle sky with a dynamic atmosphere sky shader, completely eliminates banding, layers etc. And adds new lots of new details into the sky.\nWe made a lot of changes in the timecycle as well, to match the new sky colors, means that Enhanced version of the mod will depend on this shader.\n\nAll these features are also planned for Legacy, and will be ported in the next months",
